FBIS4-36763 "drnes114_l_94007" FBIS-NES-94-114 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 ISRAEL Officials Reportedly To Boycott Italian Neofascists Officials Reportedly To Boycott Italian Neofascists TA1306191994 Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network in Hebrew 1700 GMT 13 Jun 94 TA1306191994 Jerusalem New Channel 2 Television Network Hebrew BFN [Text] Israel has decided to boycott the neofascist ministers in Italy, but will not announce this decision publicly. Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres told his Italian counterpart Antonio Martino in Luxembourg this evening that Israel will not take any steps against the Italian Government in the wake of the neofascist ministers' appointment.
